graph TB
    ExecutionPlan[ExecutionPlan Generated] --> ApprovalGate[approval_gate_node]

    ApprovalGate --> Analyzer{Analyze Plan<br/>6 HITL Types}

    Analyzer --> CheckPlan{Plan Approval<br/>Required?}
    Analyzer --> CheckClarification{Clarification<br/>Needed?}
    Analyzer --> CheckDestructive{Destructive<br/>Actions? ≥3 items}
    Analyzer --> CheckForEach{FOR_EACH<br/>Bulk Mutation?}
    Analyzer --> CheckDraft{Email/Event<br/>Draft?}
    Analyzer --> CheckModifier{Modifier<br/>Review?}

    CheckPlan -->|Yes| PlanApproval[Plan Approval<br/>Show plan summary]
    CheckClarification -->|Yes| ClarificationService[Clarification<br/>Missing info detected]
    CheckDestructive -->|Yes| DestructiveConfirm[DestructiveConfirmation<br/>Severity: CRITICAL]
    CheckForEach -->|Yes| ForEachConfirm[ForEachConfirmation<br/>Severity: WARNING]
    CheckDraft -->|Yes| DraftCritique[DraftCritique<br/>Email/Event preview]
    CheckModifier -->|Yes| ModifierReview[ModifierReview<br/>Parameter changes]

    CheckPlan -->|No| DirectExecution
    CheckClarification -->|No| DirectExecution
    CheckDestructive -->|No| DirectExecution
    CheckForEach -->|No| DirectExecution
    CheckDraft -->|No| DirectExecution
    CheckModifier -->|No| DirectExecution

    PlanApproval --> HITLDispatch
    ClarificationService --> HITLDispatch
    DestructiveConfirm --> HITLDispatch
    ForEachConfirm --> HITLDispatch
    DraftCritique --> HITLDispatch
    ModifierReview --> HITLDispatch

    HITLDispatch[hitl_dispatch_node<br/>GraphInterrupt]

    HITLDispatch --> SeverityCheck{Severity Level}

    SeverityCheck -->|INFO| UserNotification[User Notification<br/>Can Skip]
    SeverityCheck -->|WARNING| UserConfirm[User Confirmation<br/>Required]
    SeverityCheck -->|CRITICAL| UserMustReview[User Must Review<br/>& Approve]

    UserNotification --> UserDecision
    UserConfirm --> UserDecision
    UserMustReview --> UserDecision

    UserDecision{User Decision}

    UserDecision -->|Approved| TaskExecution[task_orchestrator_node<br/>Execute Plan]
    UserDecision -->|Rejected| Cancelled[End: Cancelled]
    UserDecision -->|Modified / Edited| Replanning[Back to planner_node_v3]
    UserDecision -->|Clarification Provided| Replanning

    Replanning --> ApprovalGate

    DirectExecution[Direct Execution<br/>No HITL Required] --> TaskExecution

    TaskExecution --> ExecutionComplete[Execution Complete<br/>→ response_node]

    subgraph "Multi-Channel Delivery"
        direction LR
        WebSSE[Web SSE<br/>Always]
        TelegramKB[Telegram<br/>Inline Keyboard]
        FCMPush[FCM Push<br/>If enabled]
    end

    HITLDispatch --> WebSSE
    HITLDispatch --> TelegramKB
    HITLDispatch --> FCMPush

    style ApprovalGate fill:#ffe1e1
    style DestructiveConfirm fill:#ffcccc
    style ForEachConfirm fill:#ffcccc
    style DraftCritique fill:#fff4e1
    style ModifierReview fill:#fff4e1
    style ClarificationService fill:#e1f5ff
    style PlanApproval fill:#e1f5ff
    style HITLDispatch fill:#ffe1e1
    style UserMustReview fill:#ff9999
    style TaskExecution fill:#e1ffe1
    style DirectExecution fill:#e1ffe1
